PRODUCT DESCRIPTION

Castrol Transmax? Import Multi-Vehicle Automatic Transmission Fluid is for use in most Honda, Toyota, Nissan and other imported vehicles. It exceeds the requirements of the JASO-1A performance standard created by Japanese Automobile Manufacturers. This standard is recognized by Japanese OEMs in certifying ATF for use in their vehicles.

  • Superb low temperature fluidity for cold weather shifting.
  • Exceeds all passenger car and light truck manufacturer&apos;s warranty requirements for vehicles, transmissions or power steering service where a DEXRON-IIIH, MERCON or MERCON V type ATF is specified. Not for use where MERCON SP or MERCON LV is required. Not for use where DEXRON VI is required.
  • Exceptional high temperature protection to effectively resist fluid oxidation.
  • Enhanced friction durability for smooth transmission performance.
  • Meets or exceeds General Motors DEXRON®-IIIH requirements
  • Meets or exceeds Ford MERCON® V and Ford MERCON® requirements
